[
  {"word":"abate","pos":"v","ja":"弱まる、和らげる","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"/əˈbeɪt/","ex":"The storm finally began to abate after midnight.","exJa":"嵐はついに真夜中過ぎに弱まり始めた。","collocations":["fears abate","abate slightly","gradually abate"],"synonyms":["subside","wane","diminish"],"distractorHint":["急激に強まる","完全に消滅する","突然起こる"]},
