  {"word":"abhor","pos":"v","ja":"ひどく嫌う","level":4,"cat":"general","ipa":"/əbˈhɔːr/","ex":"She abhors any form of cruelty toward animals.","exJa":"彼女は動物への残酷な行為をひどく嫌う。","collocations":["abhor violence","utterly abhor","abhor the idea"],"synonyms":["detest","loathe","despise"],"distractorHint":["熱望する","無視する","同情する"]},
